  <title>Descriptive Statistics </title>

  <introduction>
        <p> In this chapter we will investigate multiple ways to describe the data with graphs and numerical statistics. </p>
      </introduction> 

      <objectives>
        <introduction>
          <p>
            At the end of this chapter you will able to:
          </p>
        </introduction>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p> Graph data appropriately. </p> </li>
            <li> <p> Describe the center of the data with mean, median, mode. </p>
          </li>
          <li> <p> Describe the spread of a data set with range, interquartile-range, and standard deviation. </p> </li>
        </ol>
      </objectives>

